_sText:
This is a defuse map based on a cs_hockey as some one asked for a defuse version, it is modified a fair bit to make it work but retains a lot of the original paths. I spent a year off and on working on this, it includes many custom textures and detailed brushwork. I further optimized this map and framerates are great, excellent for 32 player size server. Some features of the map:

-Full HDR
-40 Players
-Custom textures
-3D skybox
-Custom sound and soundscape
-Fully tweaked nav file
-Overview and radar overview
-All content bsp zipped

Thanks to my friend Furyo for help with render problems and areaportals, visit him at www.froughol.com
